{"tid":1310644,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]連登仔有無野同絕食咗200個鐘嘅海富陳伯講？有無野想問？","createTime":"2019-07-12T18:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T13:22:34.000Z","uid":65210,"like":79,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"09c7389c2419124be1b94ec6796f2acf32bca796","tid":1310644,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:43:14.000Z","msg":"原post <br />\n[求助要人]海富73歲陳伯已絕食9日超過200小時 隻腳有傷口未埋口 點解無人知無人理！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1310102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1310102</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n以下係反送中絕食者分享TG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hungerstrike_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhungerstrike_hk&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=95d01991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hungerstrike_hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反送中絕食行動由上星期三3/7開始<br />\n參與絕食者<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>已經絕食9日 超過200小時</strong></span><br />\n今個星期三10/7夜晚20:00其實開過記者會 <br />\n記者會上有絕食宣言 並宣佈會無限期絕食<br />\n可惜記者會欠缺主流媒體採訪<br />\n令到社會大眾 以致係同路人都唔清楚海富有一班絕食者努力緊<br />\n當中絕食者陳伯 以73歲高齡加上腳傷<br />\n依然堅持全絕食 已經過咗9日！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">伯伯為咗記者會一晚無瞓！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係記者會喊住咁講咗佢嘅絕食原因 同感受！<br />\n好似無人知咁<br />\n因為無人拍到片！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地幾個連登仔睇唔過眼 決定聽日晏就自己去採訪陳伯同其他絕食者<br />\n無論條片蘋果肯要 定100毛肯要<br />\n或者冇媒體肯要<br />\n無人要就連登開Post見<br />\n73歲嘅伯伯為咗救班後生願意無限期絕食<br />\n我地唔可以比伯伯同其他絕食者白費心機<br />\n為呢場運動付出咗咁多都無人知<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以<br />\n有無野想問陳伯！<br />\n留底你嘅問題或者心聲<br />\n留底你嘅問題或者心聲<br />\n留底你嘅問題或者心聲</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星期一呢班絕食者會有苦行 <br />\n你可以笑佢地膠 笑佢地嘥心機<br />\n但兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n苦行上禮賓詳情：<br />\n日期：2019年7 月15日 (星期一)<br />\n起步時間：晚上六點半<br />\n起步地點：海富絕食站 - 金鐘海富地鐵站A出口<br />\n<br />\n*由於參加者有殘障、年長、以及絕食超過十二日之人士上斜路到禮賓府，我們需要大量義工及推輪椅者同行，請代為向大眾呼籲到以下連結成為我們的支援者：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/AByV3fw7ez11f7B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FAByV3fw7ez11f7B3&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=5e06d306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/AByV3fw7ez11f7B3</a></span>"},{"pid":"62970a475a2e54d0a01d8c9c05c978151563eb26","tid":1310644,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:48:32.000Z","msg":"好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家記得上水，沙田，金鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d8e7818b0b91131ebd38248f4552b0b33e7db3","tid":1310644,"uid":222646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:48:59.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"136aeb330067529092207fb4ed1049c49eadc2f2","tid":1310644,"uid":34063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:49:28.000Z","msg":"[713光復上水]上水站封站後處理 &amp;  北區不要前往地方指引<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1310623\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1310623</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c67f9fcb3df6f04b9e9380b209208f3104fcb3ba","tid":1310644,"uid":149844,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:50:16.000Z","msg":"多謝伯伯你嘅付出<br />\n我地雖然無同你一齊絕食<br />\n但係兄弟爬山,各有各做<br />\n同路人要一齊加油呀！"},{"pid":"7c450a669948c488c60bdd6607011fa62ff52984","tid":1310644,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:50:51.000Z","msg":"大家都知道佢心意，但見到佢咁樣真係好心痛"},{"pid":"3c3e9ce39d62623ff38aa1e29809ed01240daffd","tid":1310644,"uid":175471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:51:00.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58faba9d00b397d48a2e614c15cd7555afef3cb","tid":1310644,"uid":189489,"like":6,"dislike":0,